{
  "texts": [
    "A new study addresses unsupervised learning with WGAN [29] that works on learning a probability distribution and probability density.",
    "This is frequently accomplished by creating a parametric family of densities (Pθ)θ∈Rd.",
    "AttnGAN [30] by Xu et al.",
    "offers attentiondriven, multi-stage refining for fine-grained text-to-image creation.",
    "The AttnGAN uses a unique attentional generative network to synthesise fine-grained features in different subregions of the picture by paying attention to important words in the natural language description."
  ]
}